Hey Yellow.

 It’s your day. The day we celebrate the bright,glowing gift that you are. I almost have no words outside of “thank you”. Thank you for being my most dependable friend. Thank you for really loving me and not just my talents. Thank you for not using me. Thank you for not taking from me. Thank you for reciprocating. Thank you for communicating when you need space and for honoring my requests the same way. Thank you for BEING THERE!!! Thank you for showing me what a Best Friend is. Thank you for your support without being asked. I’m thankful I never had to beg you to be good to me. I can say without guilt, hesitation, and without fear of regret or embarrassment, you are my BEST friend. I love you so much!! It’s time to party!! Happy Birthday Yellow! 💛🔐🐘🦉

#33 treated me well! I learned to REALLY like who I am and fell in love with the process of knowing myself. I mean… I’m pretty damn cool!!! Lol! Today, I am #34. #34 represents MORE! So, here’s to MORE! MORE luxury! MORE laughs! MORE love! MORE peace! MORE stamps in my passport! MORE reasons to celebrate! MORE living! MORE Veuve! MORE fun! MORE wisdom! MORE ME! 

To MORE! 🍾🥂✨
#VEUVEandVIBES #HappyBirthdayToMe #KP34 #123

You know I’m extremely independent and surrendering to help is something I’m still working on but you’re sooo patient with me in moments of frustration. Your warmth and assiduous care keeps me cool and calm. Thanks for everything! Love you gworl! 🥂✨

I took this clip of the sky while on a flight from Savannah, GA to say goodbye to a dear friend of mine. After going nonstop and dealing with the woes and wows of life, once I saw the clouds I was able to finally… breathe. All is well. All will be well. Just don’t forget to breathe. 💛
WE ARE STILL UNDER AN OPEN HEAVEN.
